  <div style="font-family:var(--font-b);font-weight:700;color:rgba(168,230,255,0.8);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:4px;">🏔 Ice Kingdom Wars 🏔</div>
  <div class="ld-wrap"><div class="ld-bar"></div></div>
